WEBVTT

00:00:00.166 --> 00:00:02.869
The Department will normally complete its review and approval

00:00:02.936 --> 00:00:06.940
of an Employee's eligibility for a career ladder promotion on or

00:00:07.006 --> 00:00:11.277
before the 30th calendar day after he or she completes one

00:00:11.344 --> 00:00:13.113
year in the current grade level.

00:00:13.179 --> 00:00:17.117
If the review and approval for an Employee is delayed beyond

00:00:17.183 --> 00:00:20.820
the 30th calendar day and it is determined that he or she

00:00:20.887 --> 00:00:24.924
qualified for a promotion, the promotion will be retroactive to

00:00:24.991 --> 00:00:29.062
the beginning of the first pay period after requirements were met.

00:00:29.129 --> 00:00:32.098
This provision is consistent with laws that include the Back

00:00:32.165 --> 00:00:38.471
Pay Act and 5 USC 5596, as well as government-wide regulations

00:00:38.538 --> 00:00:39.906
and VA policy.


